---
import '@fontsource/inter/300.css';
import '@fontsource/inter/400.css';
import '@fontsource/inter/500.css';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>about — senja studio</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="absolute top-4 left-12 z-10">
			<a href="/" class="block text-lg leading-tight font-normal" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #1c1c1c; text-transform: uppercase;">senja studio</a>
			<p class="mt-1 text-sm font-[325]" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: #aeaeae;"><a href="/hotels" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#1c1c1c] hover:underline">hotels and stays</a> / <a href="/food" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#1c1c1c] hover:underline">food and spaces</a> / <a href="/outdoors" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#1c1c1c] hover:underline">outdoors</a> / <a href="/ugc" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#1c1c1c] hover:underline">user generated content</a></p>
			<p class="text-sm font-[325]" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: #aeaeae;"><a href="/about" class="text-[#1c1c1c] underline">about</a> / <a href="/contact" class="transition-colors hover:text-[#1c1c1c] hover:underline">contact</a></p>
		</div>

		<a href="/" class="absolute top-4 right-6 z-10 text-lg leading-tight font-normal text-[#1c1c1c] transition-colors hover:text-neutral-300" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">✕</a>


		<main class="min-h-screen px-6 pb-24 pt-28">
			<div class="ml-[29vw] max-w-xl space-y-6 text-justify text-sm font-[325] leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: #1c1c1c;">
				<p><span class="font-medium">Senja Studio</span> creates visual content for hotels, restaurants, concept stores and alternative venues across Southeast Asia and beyond.</p>
				<p>In a world saturated with images, what makes people stop is feeling. The opportunity to lose oneself in another storyline. Every project is built around storytelling first: the texture, the details, the light that carry emotion and leave a mark. Shot across multiple formats, the work holds the grain and depth that polished production cannot replicate, and that audiences instinctively trust.</p>
				<p>All content delivered within 5 business days. Full usage rights included. Ready to post.</p>
				<div class="space-y-0.5 pt-6">
					<p class="text-sm lowercase font-medium" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Destinations</p>
					<p>Based in Southeast Asia, available worldwide.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-0.5 pt-6">
					<p class="text-sm lowercase font-medium" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">My kit</p>
					<p>A mix of professional mobile equipment, drone and vintage digital cameras — chosen for the grain, texture and depth they bring to every shoot.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
